# Training Academy Management System

**Odoo Version:** 18.0

A comprehensive Odoo module for managing training academies, courses, student enrollments, and instructor assignments.

---

## Features

**Courses**

Course management with categories, auto-uppercase course codes, and enrollment capacity tracking (enrolled_count, available_seats, is_full). Workflow: Draft → Published → In Progress → Done/Cancelled. Smart buttons showing enrollment statistics. Validations: unique codes, valid dates, positive capacity.

**Enrollments**

Student course registration with grade and attendance tracking (0-100%). Workflow: Draft → Confirmed → Completed/Cancelled. Prevents duplicate enrollments and full course registrations. Kanban view grouped by state.

**Partner Extension**

Student/Instructor role flags with smart buttons for enrolled/teaching courses. Relationship tracking between students, instructors, and courses.

**Security**

Students can view published courses and manage own enrollments. Instructors have full course management with read-only enrollments. Managers have full system access.

---

## Installation

1. Apps → Update Apps List
2. Search "Academy"
3. Activate

---

## Usage

**Students**

Browse courses: Academy → Courses → Courses

Enroll in courses: Academy → Enrollments → My Enrollments → New

Track grades and attendance in enrollment records

**Instructors**

Manage courses with workflow buttons (Publish, Start, Complete, Cancel)

View enrollments via smart button (read-only access)

**Managers**

Full access to all records and configuration menu

User management and system administration

---

## Module Structure

academy/
├── models/ # Python models (course, enrollment, category, partner)
├── views/ # XML views and menus
├── security/ # Groups, rules, access rights
└── static/ # Icons and assets

```

### **Key Models:**

academy.course - Courses with workflow and capacity tracking

academy.enrollment - Student enrollments with grades

academy.course.category - Course categorization

res.partner - Extended with student/instructor roles

---

## Testing

Create course with auto-uppercase code

Enroll student in available course

Verify enrollment in full course fails

Check duplicate enrollment prevention

Test course workflow transitions

Verify computed fields (enrolled_count, available_seats)

Confirm security rules per role
```
